Ctrl c         Copy
Ctrl x         Cut
Ctrl v         Paste
Ctrl+Shift v   Paste (as plain text)
     Del       Delete
Ctrl Backspace Delete word left
Ctrl Del       Delete word right
Ctrl Left      One word left
Ctrl Right     One word right
     Home      Move to BOL
     End       Move to EOL
Ctrl Home      Move to beginning of text
Ctrl End       Move to end of text
Ctrl z         Undo
Ctrl y         Redo
Ctrl a         Select all
